    "SessionKey": "2019R1",
    "MeasurePrefix": "HB",
    "MeasureNumber": 5027,
    "CatchLine": "Appropriates moneys from General Fund to Department of Land Conservation and Development for certain biennial expenses.",
    "MinorityCatchLine": null,
    "MeasureSummary": "\tAppropriates moneys from General Fund to Department of Land Conservation and Development for certain biennial expenses. \n\tLimits certain biennial expenditures from fees, moneys or other revenues, including Miscellaneous Receipts, but excluding lottery funds and federal funds, collected or received by department. \n\tLimits biennial expenditures by department from federal funds. \n\tDeclares emergency, effective July 1, 2019.",
    "CurrentVersion": "A",
    "RelatingToFull": "Relating to the financial administration of the Department of Land Conservation and Development; and declaring an emergency.",
